OL,3,CLast plea as union urges oil refinery
OL,4,Cworkers to be furloughed
OL,6,FA union is urging the government to
OL,7,Ffurlough workers as they finish their
OL,8,Flast day of work at an oil refinery in
OL,9,FLincolnshire.
OL,11,F125 employees at Lindsey Oil Refinery,
OL,12,Fnear Immingham, were made redundant
OL,13,Fafter owner Prax Group went into
OL,14,Fadministration in July. The site was
OL,15,Ftaken over by the Official Receiver.
OL,17,FUnite Union are calling for the
OL,18,Fworkers to be furloughed to preserve
OL,19,Fjobs and production until a buyer is
OL,20,Ffound.
