OL,3,CLast plea as union urges oil refinery
OL,4,Cworkers to be furloughed
OL,6,FThe refinery supports 420 directly
OL,7,Femployed workers plus another 500
OL,8,Fcontract jobs and potentially
OL,9,Fthousands in the supply chain.
OL,11,FAbout 255 employees will remain at the
OL,12,Fsite after redundant staff finish
OL,13,Ftheir last shifts.
OL,15,FThe government says the search for a
OL,16,Fnew buyer is ongoing.
OL,18,FEnergy Minister Michael Shanks
OL,19,Fconfirmed there was no buyers in place
OL,20,Fto keep employees on.
