OL,3,CLast plea as union urges oil refinery
OL,4,Cworkers to be furloughed
OL,6,F"Our thoughts are with the workers,
OL,7,Ftheir families and the community who
OL,8,Fhave been badly let down by Prax
OL,9,FLindsey Oil Refinery's owners.
OL,11,F"While the majority of the workforce
OL,12,Fis being retained - the Official
OL,13,FReceiver has confirmed there are no
OL,14,Foffers on the table that would see a
OL,15,Freturn to refining operations in the
OL,16,Fnear term to allow for all employees
OL,17,Fto be retained.
