OL,3,CLast plea as union urges oil refinery
OL,4,Cworkers to be furloughed
OL,6,FLast month, the government said it
OL,7,Fwill take immediate action to fund a
OL,8,FTraining Guarantee for refinery
OL,9,Fworkers to support them to find new,
OL,10,Fsecure, long-term jobs, including in
OL,11,Fthe clean energy workforce.
OL,13,FThe Insolvency Service said it will
OL,14,Fsupport employees made redundant
OL,15,Fthrough a Redundancy Payment Service.
OL,17,FThe conduct of the company and its
OL,18,Fdirectors remains the subject of an
OL,19,Fongoing Insolvency Service
OL,20,Finvestigation.
